{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01KzxBH8uhL3vTkjeD8kFHZi","type":"tool_result","content":"   430→## CLI Reference\n   431→\n   432→Every subcommand supports `--help` (or `-h`) to show detailed usage, flags, and\n   433→examples. Use `cloche help <command>` for the same output:\n   434→\n   435→```\n   436→cloche --help              # top-level overview\n   437→cloche help run            # detailed help for \"run\"\n   438→cloche run --help          # same as above\n   439→```\n   440→\n   441→### `cloche init`\n   442→\n   443→Scaffold a new Cloche project.\n   444→\n   445→```\n   446→cloche init [--workflow <name>] [--base-image <base>]\n   447→```\n   448→\n   449→| Flag | Default | Description |\n   450→|------|---------|-------------|\n   451→| `--workflow <name>` | `develop` | Workflow name. Creates `.cloche/<name>.cloche`. |\n   452→| `--base-image <base>` | `cloche-base:latest` | Base Docker image for the generated Dockerfile. |\n   453→\n   454→Creates `.cloche/` with workflow file, Dockerfile, `config.toml`, prompt templates,\n   455→host workflow (`host.cloche`), and prompt generation script. Skips existing files.\n   456→\n   457→### `cloche run`\n   458→\n   459→Launch a workflow run."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5c40c135-d6d6-46ff-91b7-1e8ee6d44e10","uuid":"75ed7616-c731-4a20-951e-b95f2dbee588","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/docs/USAGE.md","content":"## CLI Reference\n\nEvery subcommand supports `--help` (or `-h`) to show detailed usage, flags, and\nexamples. Use `cloche help <command>` for the same output:\n\n```\ncloche --help              # top-level overview\ncloche help run            # detailed help for \"run\"\ncloche run --help          # same as above\n```\n\n### `cloche init`\n\nScaffold a new Cloche project.\n\n```\ncloche init [--workflow <name>] [--base-image <base>]\n```\n\n| Flag | Default | Description |\n|------|---------|-------------|\n| `--workflow <name>` | `develop` | Workflow name. Creates `.cloche/<name>.cloche`. |\n| `--base-image <base>` | `cloche-base:latest` | Base Docker image for the generated Dockerfile. |\n\nCreates `.cloche/` with workflow file, Dockerfile, `config.toml`, prompt templates,\nhost workflow (`host.cloche`), and prompt generation script. Skips existing files.\n\n### `cloche run`\n\nLaunch a workflow run.","numLines":30,"startLine":430,"totalLines":664}}}
